    %% Permissions to Foundry resource
    User -- "Azure AI Project Manager" --> F
    User -- "Cognitive Services OpenAI Contributor" --> F

    SMI -- "Cognitive Services OpenAI User" --> F

    %% Runtime flow
    Agents --> FP
    FP --> AS
    AS --> SA
    AS --> F
```

